channel.title: The MoparScape Client (ItemID's and the like..)
channel.description:
Okay, so I have the MoparScape client. I want to find an item ID, so I go to to Help > ItemID's and then the items.xml opens up but it is completely blank - no items, nothing.
The same goes for all the ID menu's.
